1
00:00:00,410 --> 00:00:02,460
Quit screwin' around, Laxus!

2
00:00:02,460 --> 00:00:04,450
Get serious!

3
00:00:04,450 --> 00:00:06,100
What's he doing?

4
00:00:06,100 --> 00:00:07,830
<i>Laxus</i> is getting beaten up?

5
00:00:08,430 --> 00:00:10,190
Something doesn't feel right about this...

6
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,600
I don't sense anything

7
00:00:12,610 --> 00:00:16,480
coming from that Alexei-san, though...

8
00:00:17,710 --> 00:00:21,160
Oh, boy! What a one-sided development!

9
00:00:21,160 --> 00:00:25,450
Is this as far as it goes for Fairy Tail B
 team and Laxus's tale of triumph?!

10
00:00:25,710 --> 00:00:30,420
It's devastating, really... He's 
showing such great strength.

11
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:33,420
And yet I'm not sensing much magic power.

12
00:00:33,750 --> 00:00:36,480
Perhaps it means he's not going all out yet?

13
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:14,400
Is that really Laxus?

14
00:02:14,690 --> 00:02:18,680
The impression I got of him from 
you is totally different, Happy.

15
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:23,990
He does have a connection with that guild's 
master, so maybe it's making him hesitant.

16
00:02:24,090 --> 00:02:25,950
This isn't like you,

17
00:02:25,950 --> 00:02:28,000
Laxus!

18
00:02:32,990 --> 00:02:35,960
Anti-Fairy Tail guild?

19
00:02:36,270 --> 00:02:37,720
That's right!

20
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:45,280
Made up of Wizards who are masters at all 
of the Fairy Tail members' weaknesses.

21
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:48,480
And the four of us are the guild's elite.

22
00:02:49,100 --> 00:02:52,120
Do you intend to go to war with us?

23
00:02:54,070 --> 00:02:57,710
We know every detail of your weaknesses.

24
00:02:57,710 --> 00:03:03,110
Shall I release the power that my guild has 
been accumulating these past seven years?

25
00:03:04,530 --> 00:03:08,160
Gramps has already done a 
thorough investigation of you.

26
00:03:11,420 --> 00:03:13,050
Ivan...

27
00:03:13,370 --> 00:03:14,990
Laxus...

28
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:20,410
Wendy vs. Cheria!

29
00:03:30,180 --> 00:03:31,980
A thorough investigation, you say?

30
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:34,130
Do I have to say it again?

31
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:38,930
The number of members, your 
guild's location, funding...

32
00:03:38,930 --> 00:03:43,070
We know everything that's been 
going on these seven years.

33
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:44,170
What?!

34
00:03:44,170 --> 00:03:47,500
It was Gajeel! He tricked us!

35
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:53,120
He seemed like a nasty fellow, and 
I guess that impression was correct.

36
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:55,490
Then he was a double agent?

37
00:03:55,490 --> 00:04:00,440
He doesn't seem to be one for fine 
details, but it backfired on us.

38
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,960
What the hell?! Why is 
he havin' a tough time?!

39
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:07,870
Stupid Laxus... What, does 
he have a cold?! Crap.

40
00:04:07,870 --> 00:04:12,250
Are those bastards talkin' trash about me?

41
00:04:12,250 --> 00:04:15,500
An anti-Fairy Tail guild?

42
00:04:15,690 --> 00:04:21,210
I already have info on my 
foolish son and his wizards,

43
00:04:21,210 --> 00:04:24,820
but I don't have a precise 
report yet on some of them.

44
00:04:24,870 --> 00:04:27,350
Particularly that Alexei person...

45
00:04:27,350 --> 00:04:30,840
I have no information on his 
existence, let alone his background.

46
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:33,070
But isn't that strange?

47
00:04:33,090 --> 00:04:36,790
Considering all of our secrets have been 
leaked, he hasn't really had any reaction.

48
00:04:37,020 --> 00:04:40,800
Even though Gramps knew all that, 
he didn't make a move on you.

49
00:04:45,550 --> 00:04:47,370
Hey, Gramps...

50
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:50,160
Are you sure it's okay to let them be?

51
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:55,100
You said my old man had information 
that could be damaging to Fairy Tail.

52
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:58,470
Seven years have passed since then.

53
00:04:58,470 --> 00:04:59,750
But still...

54
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:05,110
During those seven years, there's been 
no sign any of that info has leaked.

55
00:05:05,470 --> 00:05:08,120
You can't be sure of that.

56
00:05:08,380 --> 00:05:10,960
No. I'm certain.

57
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:16,370
They're well aware of how dangerous that 
information could be if it gets out.

58
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:20,460
What is that information, anyway?

59
00:05:21,100 --> 00:05:23,110
You're better off not knowing.

60
00:05:23,390 --> 00:05:26,970
Every guild has their forbidden secrets.

61
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:32,160
I've heard that in these seven years,

62
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:37,380
Ivan hasn't been up to any mischief 
or done anything to harm our members.

63
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:43,320
As long as he doesn't make a move, I have 
no intention of stirring anything up either.

64
00:05:49,450 --> 00:05:50,490
Maybe...

65
00:05:51,330 --> 00:05:56,670
...somewhere in Gramps' 
heart, he had faith in you.

66
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:01,210
Because you're father and son...

67
00:06:02,230 --> 00:06:04,510
Silence!

68
00:06:08,980 --> 00:06:12,840
I've been waiting all this time for this day!

69
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:16,600
It was all to get Lumen Histoire!

70
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:22,990
I did your guild no harm for 
seven years? Of course not!

71
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:27,960
There's no way the dregs you left 
behind had any information on that!

72
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:31,360
Inside your guild, Magnolia, Tenroujima, too!

73
00:06:31,360 --> 00:06:34,870
I searched every place 
associated with your guild!

74
00:06:34,870 --> 00:06:37,170
But I still didn't find anything!

75
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:43,750
Where is Lumen Histoire?! Where is it?!

76
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:48,880
Tell me, Laxus! You're my son, aren't you?!

77
00:06:53,040 --> 00:06:55,640
Even if it's for the sake of family,

78
00:06:55,640 --> 00:07:00,820
the guild can't stand by if the 
lives of its members are threatened.

79
00:07:01,030 --> 00:07:04,520
That's how the previous master 
protected this guild, too.

80
00:07:04,520 --> 00:07:06,660
That's Fairy Tail.

81
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:10,530
The guild is our family!

82
00:07:10,530 --> 00:07:13,350
It's our place to go home to!

83
00:07:20,310 --> 00:07:22,830
I thought you were standing 
there a little too quietly...

84
00:07:23,040 --> 00:07:26,050
You were taking measure 
of my magic, were you?

85
00:07:26,050 --> 00:07:28,710
That part of you never changes.

86
00:07:28,710 --> 00:07:32,850
Or is it just that you can't bring 
yourself to hit your father?

87
00:07:32,850 --> 00:07:36,860
You're such a nice boy, Laxus-chan.

88
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:39,060
Laxus!

89
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:06,550
Obra! Do it!

90
00:08:06,550 --> 00:08:07,850
Extinguish his magic!

91
00:08:07,850 --> 00:08:13,150
Now, unleash the power of 
the anti-Fairy Tail guild!

92
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:19,780
Is this the guy who 
attacked Wendy and Carla?!

93
00:08:23,100 --> 00:08:24,690
Scarlet Hair!

94
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:28,570
Needle Blast!

95
00:08:28,790 --> 00:08:31,990
This is for Gray!

96
00:08:35,300 --> 00:08:37,530
Gotcha!

97
00:08:38,370 --> 00:08:42,160
This is for Lucy!

98
00:08:45,490 --> 00:08:46,780
It can't be...

99
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,660
Sand Fake!

100
00:08:51,700 --> 00:08:53,380
You...

101
00:08:53,850 --> 00:08:55,490
I don't understand.

102
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:59,180
M-My elite team!

103
00:08:59,570 --> 00:09:00,930
Damn you, old man!

104
00:09:02,220 --> 00:09:05,100
I don't know what it is you're after,

105
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:08,860
but you're gonna pay for hurting my comrades!

106
00:09:08,860 --> 00:09:13,060
W-Wait! I'm your father!

107
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:17,360
We're family! You would hit your own father?!

108
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:20,830
My family is Fairy Tail!

109
00:09:20,830 --> 00:09:24,000
You ungrateful wretch!

110
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,670
Begone!

111
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:29,890
I crush

112
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:33,210
my family's enemies!

113
00:09:46,330 --> 00:09:48,720
W-What in the world...?!

114
00:09:48,940 --> 00:09:50,970
Laxus has a twin?!

115
00:09:50,970 --> 00:09:55,650
Wrong, dumbass. Laxus disappeared 
and another Laxus appeared...

116
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:57,430
No. This is...

117
00:09:57,430 --> 00:09:58,950
Ivan...

118
00:09:59,200 --> 00:10:01,070
And the others, too...

119
00:10:01,070 --> 00:10:02,410
Don't tell me...

120
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:03,730
Thoughtforms?

121
00:10:03,730 --> 00:10:05,370
We were duped!

122
00:10:05,610 --> 00:10:09,180
But what happened here?!

123
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:12,780
That face... The guild master-kabo!

124
00:10:12,780 --> 00:10:17,010
Alexei was really Master Ivan-kabo!

125
00:10:18,950 --> 00:10:23,260
Then the battle we were watching between 
Laxus and Alexei was just an illusion?!

126
00:10:23,260 --> 00:10:28,050
Laxus is still standing! The match is over!

127
00:10:28,050 --> 00:10:32,450
So we couldn't see it, but he was 
under attack by five people...

128
00:10:32,450 --> 00:10:35,570
On top of that, the master 
participated in the tournament...

129
00:10:35,930 --> 00:10:38,970
Any way you look at it, that's 
a breach of the rules.

130
00:10:39,020 --> 00:10:42,240
That guy wiped out all of the 
Raven Tail members by himself?!

131
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:44,430
First, there was Erza, then Cana...

132
00:10:44,430 --> 00:10:47,950
Fairy Tail's full of monsters!

133
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:52,100
At any rate, the victor...

134
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:56,460
...is Laxus Dreyar from Fairy Tail B!

135
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:03,260
It's like he got payback for me...

136
00:11:04,000 --> 00:11:08,400
He beat all of 'em?! Why does 
he get to steal all the glory?!

137
00:11:08,400 --> 00:11:12,320
I just hope that Flare 
girl isn't abused again.

138
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,900
You really are a nice person...

139
00:11:15,780 --> 00:11:18,900
That was playing dirty...

140
00:11:20,300 --> 00:11:22,080
Ivan...

141
00:11:32,390 --> 00:11:35,920
Laxus... I lost this time,

142
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:38,520
but remember this...

143
00:11:39,250 --> 00:11:43,250
Lumen Histoire is Fairy Tail's darkness.

144
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:45,510
Eventually, the time will come...

145
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:49,080
...when you learn Fairy Tail's true identity.

146
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:53,670
You people are coming with us as well.

147
00:11:54,990 --> 00:11:56,180
Don't touch me!

148
00:11:56,180 --> 00:11:58,160
Enough! Come along quietly!

149
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:00,360
W-What's with this one?!

150
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,790
Stand up!

151
00:12:01,790 --> 00:12:05,750
After some consultation, it's been 
decided that Raven Tail is disqualified!

152
00:12:05,750 --> 00:12:09,240
And they're banned from participating 
in the tournament for three years.

153
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,900
Naturally!

154
00:12:13,650 --> 00:12:15,760
We'll meet again...

155
00:12:16,210 --> 00:12:18,960
...Fairy Tail.

156
00:12:26,290 --> 00:12:30,950
Well, that result was an embarrassment,

157
00:12:30,950 --> 00:12:35,940
but let's move on to our fourth match, 
the last match of the day-kabo!

158
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:39,740
From Fairy Tail A, Wendy Marvel!

159
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,550
I changed my outfit!

160
00:12:41,550 --> 00:12:42,650
Good luck!

161
00:12:42,650 --> 00:12:48,750
Versus Cheria Blendy of Lamia Scale!

162
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:49,900
I'll do my best!

163
00:12:52,820 --> 00:12:53,990
Wendy...

164
00:12:54,850 --> 00:12:58,690
It looks like they don't 
know Cheria's strength yet.

165
00:12:58,760 --> 00:13:01,590
I can just picture the look 
of surprise on Gray's face.

166
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:04,070
That's not the face I see...

167
00:13:05,120 --> 00:13:08,450
Laxus got revenge for my sock!

168
00:13:08,450 --> 00:13:10,470
What am I doing?

169
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,830
Give it your all.

170
00:13:12,830 --> 00:13:13,700
Right!

171
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:16,980
If you lose, you're gonna 
spin. You know that, right?

172
00:13:16,980 --> 00:13:19,410
Alright, the moment you've been waiting for!

173
00:13:19,410 --> 00:13:23,320
Both contestants are taking the field-kabo!

174
00:13:29,350 --> 00:13:32,230
U-Um, are you okay?!

175
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,460
N-Nice to meet you...

176
00:13:41,890 --> 00:13:43,210
Same here!

177
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:45,930
Is that girl gonna be okay?

178
00:13:46,030 --> 00:13:49,170
To me, it looks like she's got 
magic and motivation in spades!

179
00:13:49,170 --> 00:13:51,680
Knowing Wendy, I'm sure she'll be fine!

180
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:55,010
Wow. I can tell even from here...

181
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:57,960
She's improved enormously 
compared to seven years ago.

182
00:13:58,330 --> 00:13:59,510
But still...

183
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:03,160
That Cheria girl's magic...

184
00:14:04,020 --> 00:14:07,490
This is sure to be an 
incredibly cute showdown!

185
00:14:07,490 --> 00:14:11,090
I'm rootin' for 'em both-pyon!

186
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:12,190
"Pyon"?

187
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,370
Your character's changed...

188
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:19,710
Ul... This magic...

189
00:14:19,890 --> 00:14:20,910
Yeah...

190
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:23,840
Zeref...?

191
00:14:24,300 --> 00:14:26,770
Jellal! You felt that, didn't you?!

192
00:14:27,070 --> 00:14:28,380
In the arena?

193
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:31,670
Ultear, Meldy, stand by! Don't move!

194
00:14:31,670 --> 00:14:32,800
Understood!

195
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:35,420
Be careful!

196
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:40,580
Alright, the final match of day three!

197
00:14:41,650 --> 00:14:43,860
Begin!

198
00:14:45,250 --> 00:14:47,570
Good luck, Wendy.

199
00:14:47,860 --> 00:14:51,570
See Cheria's ability and be stunned, Gray.

200
00:14:51,590 --> 00:14:54,470
Don't underestimate Wendy, Lyon.

201
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:59,730
Truly a cute combination! I'm tickled pink!

202
00:14:59,730 --> 00:15:02,560
Was that girl in Fairy Tail?

203
00:15:02,560 --> 00:15:05,890
Yes. I only know a little about her,

204
00:15:05,980 --> 00:15:08,170
but she's a very courageous wizard.

205
00:15:08,170 --> 00:15:11,630
After all my training, I 
have to do my best here!

206
00:15:11,880 --> 00:15:13,170
Here I go!

207
00:15:13,890 --> 00:15:15,300
Ready!

208
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:18,650
Arms, Vernier... Enchant!

209
00:15:19,600 --> 00:15:22,400
Wing Slash of the Sky Dragon!

210
00:15:23,560 --> 00:15:24,770
She dodged it?!

211
00:15:24,770 --> 00:15:28,780
North wind, become the breath of 
the gods and blow on the land!

212
00:15:28,780 --> 00:15:31,360
God of the Sky, Boreas!

213
00:15:32,470 --> 00:15:33,410
Wendy!

214
00:15:33,410 --> 00:15:34,640
Black wind?!

215
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:35,920
She's...

216
00:15:40,100 --> 00:15:43,410
Wow! You dodged that, huh?

217
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:44,950
In that case...

218
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:52,010
Wind! Wind! Bore through the ground 
and make it dance up to the sky!

219
00:15:52,010 --> 00:15:53,930
Dance of the Sky God!

220
00:15:56,180 --> 00:15:57,850
I'm not done!

221
00:16:00,240 --> 00:16:02,080
Talons of the Sky Dragon!

222
00:16:05,860 --> 00:16:07,630
Roar...

223
00:16:08,250 --> 00:16:09,730
Howl...

224
00:16:09,730 --> 00:16:11,860
I don't believe it! That brat...

225
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,530
...has the same magic as Wendy?!

226
00:16:13,530 --> 00:16:15,400
Lost Magic!

227
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:19,160
Sky God Slayer Magic...

228
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:21,040
...of the Sky Dragon!

229
00:16:21,040 --> 00:16:23,110
...of the Sky God!

230
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:32,250
Is this for real?!

231
00:16:32,250 --> 00:16:33,450
Awesome!

232
00:16:33,450 --> 00:16:34,840
Hey!

233
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:36,420
It's ferocious!

234
00:16:36,420 --> 00:16:37,900
Cut it out, Obaba.

235
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:39,780
That'll be in my dreams!

236
00:16:44,990 --> 00:16:46,620
Who are you?

237
00:16:50,060 --> 00:16:52,660
A Sky God Slayer.

238
00:16:53,850 --> 00:16:55,500
God Slayer?!

239
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,910
God Slaying Magic?!

240
00:16:59,730 --> 00:17:01,880
So that guy wasn't the only one...

241
00:17:02,200 --> 00:17:03,550
You know her?

242
00:17:03,580 --> 00:17:06,670
That one guy from Grimoire, 
Shinpachiro or something...

243
00:17:06,670 --> 00:17:09,500
Didn't he say it was Zancrow?

244
00:17:09,650 --> 00:17:12,050
He used God Slayer Magic too?

245
00:17:12,420 --> 00:17:17,150
God Slayer?! Nah, it wasn't that big a deal!

246
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:22,260
No matter who her opponent is, right 
now, Wendy has to face her on her own.

247
00:17:23,440 --> 00:17:26,100
This is Wendy's moment of truth.

248
00:17:26,850 --> 00:17:28,550
I'm surprised...

249
00:17:28,820 --> 00:17:30,690
I heard about you from Lyon.

250
00:17:30,690 --> 00:17:34,360
He said there was a girl in Fairy Tail 
who can use the same magic as me.

251
00:17:34,360 --> 00:17:36,480
Maybe I was a little too rough?

252
00:17:36,480 --> 00:17:38,890
Sorry. Did it hurt?

253
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:43,240
I'm fine. This is a battle.

254
00:17:44,350 --> 00:17:47,430
Since we're here, let's have more fun, okay?

255
00:17:48,170 --> 00:17:49,630
I...

256
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:55,110
...don't really know what it 
means to have fun fighting,

257
00:17:56,480 --> 00:17:58,840
but I'll do my best for the guild!

258
00:17:59,210 --> 00:18:01,140
I think that's fine.

259
00:18:01,160 --> 00:18:04,100
I'll do my best for love and the guild, too!

260
00:18:04,100 --> 00:18:09,560
Gadzooks! To the eye, they're as cute as can 
be, but both of them are impressive wizards!

261
00:18:09,560 --> 00:18:11,570
Your wig...

262
00:18:17,370 --> 00:18:20,820
Oh, my! Two wizards, both 
wielding Wind Magic,

263
00:18:20,820 --> 00:18:23,330
but is Cheria-tan one rank higher?!

264
00:18:23,330 --> 00:18:25,520
Cheria...tan?

265
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:28,290
Strictly speaking, it's Sky Magic.

266
00:18:31,390 --> 00:18:32,750
Everyone...

267
00:18:33,390 --> 00:18:34,750
Everyone has...

268
00:18:34,750 --> 00:18:37,110
...made it this far.

269
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:42,700
Elfman-san said the rest is up to me!

270
00:18:49,980 --> 00:18:53,360
I don't like to fight,

271
00:18:54,310 --> 00:18:58,270
but when I have to fight for 
the sake of the guild...

272
00:19:03,470 --> 00:19:06,260
...even I will do it seriously!

273
00:19:09,670 --> 00:19:12,000
So you eat air, huh?

274
00:19:12,000 --> 00:19:13,510
Then I'll do it, too!

275
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:15,950
Time to eat!

276
00:19:16,390 --> 00:19:21,200
Well, well. Who would've expected 
Cheria to eat air during a battle?

277
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:23,940
Does that mean she recognizes 
her opponent as worthy?

278
00:19:23,940 --> 00:19:27,550
Do it seriously! If you 
don't, you'll lose a sock!

279
00:19:27,550 --> 00:19:31,300
Cool it. And socks have 
nothing to do with it.

280
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:33,690
Cheria is just warming up.

281
00:19:34,140 --> 00:19:38,570
W-What are Wendy-tan and Cheria-tan doing?!

282
00:19:38,570 --> 00:19:42,280
Is it my imagination or has 
the oxygen thinned out a bit?

283
00:19:42,650 --> 00:19:44,240
Dragon Slayer's Secret Art!

284
00:19:46,030 --> 00:19:48,990
Has she already mastered them both?!

285
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:50,200
There it is!

286
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:51,500
Go!

287
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:53,440
Wendy knows the Secret Art?!

288
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,000
Incredible!

289
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:56,460
She's as good as won.

290
00:19:57,110 --> 00:19:58,750
What is this?

291
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,550
A magic wind barrier?

292
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:02,660
You've sealed us inside!

293
00:20:03,380 --> 00:20:06,310
Light Burst: Sky Drill!

294
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:21,110
Cheria!

295
00:20:21,110 --> 00:20:23,300
Yeah!

296
00:20:22,380 --> 00:20:24,030
She did it!

297
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:30,580
I haven't mastered Milky Way yet...

298
00:20:31,490 --> 00:20:34,020
...so this was my full force.

299
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,990
I used all my magic...

300
00:20:37,250 --> 00:20:39,560
W-Well, well...

301
00:20:42,490 --> 00:20:45,510
You were wonderful, Wendy.

302
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:50,100
Maybe I went overboard...

303
00:20:50,570 --> 00:20:52,070
But this way...

304
00:20:52,700 --> 00:20:54,480
Cheria's down!

305
00:20:54,480 --> 00:20:58,550
The winner, from Fairy Tail A...

306
00:20:58,550 --> 00:21:01,130
Sorry! Wait a second!

307
00:21:01,170 --> 00:21:03,310
I'm just getting started!

308
00:21:06,350 --> 00:21:09,160
You're impressive, Wendy.

309
00:21:10,050 --> 00:21:12,590
P-P-Pardon me!

310
00:21:12,590 --> 00:21:15,540
Let the match continue-kabo!

311
00:21:15,780 --> 00:21:17,400
What is she?

312
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:20,040
Look! Her wounds are gone!

313
00:21:20,530 --> 00:21:26,020
Whereas Wendy can't heal herself, 
with Sky God Slayer Magic you can.

314
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:29,760
Sorry, but she has no chance of winning this.

315
00:21:30,330 --> 00:21:32,170
What kind of girl is she?!

316
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:35,320
Damn you, Lyon... To keep 
a secret like this...

317
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:38,670
Even though I told her to give it her all...

318
00:21:38,670 --> 00:21:41,100
...she hasn't put her whole 
heart into it yet, huh?

319
00:21:41,100 --> 00:21:43,010
Just how strong is she?!

320
00:21:43,010 --> 00:21:45,770
That's my cousin!

321
00:21:45,770 --> 00:21:48,700
She's far stronger than you!

322
00:21:49,760 --> 00:21:53,030
Are you okay? Want to give up?

323
00:21:53,720 --> 00:21:54,960
Wendy...

324
00:21:56,420 --> 00:21:57,320
Excuse me.

325
00:21:57,320 --> 00:21:58,250
No problem.

326
00:22:01,520 --> 00:22:02,780
Mystogan?

327
00:22:03,320 --> 00:22:05,460
Jellal, can you hear me?

328
00:22:05,460 --> 00:22:07,950
Well? Have you found out anything?

329
00:22:07,950 --> 00:22:10,010
No, nothing yet.

330
00:22:11,210 --> 00:22:12,470
Cheria...

331
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:16,610
Don't tell me that girl 
is mixed up with Zeref...

332
00:22:18,940 --> 00:22:22,750
Oh, no! At this rate, Wendy 
will be in grave danger!

333
00:23:55,980 --> 00:24:00,600
I have a feeling Wendy and Cheria's cuteness 
ranking will go up after this match.

334
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:02,850
Certainly, people are gettin' pumped 
up about this in a weird way.

335
00:24:02,850 --> 00:24:06,570
Even though I'm younger, smaller, and 
most importantly, cuter than them both!

336
00:24:06,570 --> 00:24:08,520
Yeah, well, what difference does it make...?

337
00:24:08,520 --> 00:24:13,510
It makes a difference! There are some fights 
that I'm not willing to just let go!

338
00:24:13,970 --> 00:24:16,470
Next time: Small Fist!

339
00:24:16,860 --> 00:24:19,440
And exactly what are you fighting against?

340
00:24:19,440 --> 00:24:23,350
This world, where everyone makes a 
fuss only over people that stand out!

341
00:24:23,880 --> 00:24:24,520
Good luck!

342
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:26,920


